{
  "stem": "13981.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I actually shot pictures inside the courtroom for my own [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] enjoyment and fun or recollection, memory, memorabilia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But oftentimes I had to take the pictures, or most of the time, from the projection booth, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from where I projected the films or the stills [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of those pictures I took was of the defendants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it so happened that you only can go to-- when you are in a closed room, you cannot get the angle you always want.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I took this particular picture of the defendants.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Goering is covered up, except for his belly sticking out, by one of the guards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a pretty good picture otherwise.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So through connections, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as I mentioned before, I never went in there, had anything to do with the defendants.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the guard that guarded Hoffmann had the connection with the other guards, and he took this picture.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had it blown up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I blew it up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they're all signed except-- autographed it, except Hess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Goering, Schacht, and Franz Papen said to this guard that they didn't want to sign with the rest of the hoodlums on the same paper.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took out a little three by five card and wrote their names on it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I pasted them to the back of the picture, so that in such a way that can be flipped up, and the names underneath are fully visible.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was my camera, and I took the picture.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the projection booth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't agree with the judges to let Franz Papen go free.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
